 assessment learning and equity audience general public admission please rsvp to scope stanford edu event category lectures readings sponsor stanford center for oppurtunity and policy in education scope contact email scope stanford edu website http edpolicy stanford edu calendar news &amp events events in the spotlight school news press releases suse in the media stanford educator itunes u suse on youtube featured events march 20 screening of mitchell 20 and panel discussion 4 30 pm 6 45 pm ceras 100b april 5 school of education 2012 career fair registration is open 3 30 pm 6 00 pm tresidder union 2nd floor april 13 aera reception in vancouver bc 8 00 pm 10 00 pm the fairmont hotel vancouver event calendar stanford university school of education 485 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 3096 tel 650 723 2109 copyright 2012 stanford university all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints site map contact us helpsu suse it axess academic calendar stanford bulletin office of the registrar edmail stanfordwho stanfordyou login connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr make a gift now
